formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) As per Technical Guidance Note issued by ICAI, Interest on Partners capital has been excluded from money borrowed for construction activity and hence the amount of Interest paid figure has been much less than the estimated costs.				
2) The Unsecured Loan Details have been taken from the books as on 21/11/2019 however we have relied on managament confirmaiton of unsecured Loan outstanding and its utilization for construction of business.				
3) As per the infromation and explanation provides to us and based on our verification of data, No encumbrance has been created on any unit till the date of this Certificate.				
4)We have relined on the work of an expert who has issued form 1 and Form 2 while determing the status of proejct completion and cost incurred as shown in Form 1 & Form 2 repsectively.				
5) It is the responsibility of the Promoter of the firm to provide and verity the PAN and Mobile No. of allottees and we have relied on the data provided and verified by the Promoter of the firm.				
6) The project has been complted but the figures as shown in Actual cost incurred is less than estimated cost of consturction due to non payment of bills and non recording of bills. In the absence of unpaid bills & unrecorded bills for verificaiton, we have prepraed the Actual Construction cost incurred based on the data available on records and verificaiton thereof.				
7) It has been informed to us that in some of the allottee, Agreement to sell has not been executed as the customer has not come for agreement on specified date provided to them. We have relied on the presentation and confirmation provided by the promoter while providing date of agreement to sell.
